cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for human pose estimation from video. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of application-specific data for fine-tuning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions the use of the Kinect sensor, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper discusses the use of the method for person tracking and action recognition, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics).
